divs: Sighting Detailsme and my wife were driveing down northwest express lane,its short of a short cut on time.Anyway looking to my left over on the moutain is this huge rectagular looking thing so i ask my wife what she thought and she said it looked lke a huge r.v.and i said yeah but its bigger than the tree's around it way bigger.where it was sitting thay cleared for logging so we could see the size and shape clealy.we got to town about 12:30 and left around 2:30,3:00 p.m.on the way back it was gone.the one thing that cought my eye was how bright the u.f.o. was like a birght pice of silver hard to miss.some thing you put things into,like it held or would hold something.if you ever seen resendent evil exetion that box they had those zombies in thats what it looked like.no action's just sat there.my feelings were like why is there a box big enough to hold king kong doing sitting on the side of the moutain.lost sight driveing into town.
